    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wartheon</strong> is a fast-paced 2D roguelike adventure set in a world on the brink of elemental collapse. When the malevolent sorcerer <strong>Moldran</strong> tears open a rift to steal the powers of the elemental orders, chaos floods the land. From this rupture, twisted beasts and corrupted creatures pour into Wartheon, warping the balance of nature and plunging the world into peril.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of one of eight unique champions — each a master of their own combat style and skills — and fight your way through <strong>eight perilous levels</strong>, each dominated by a sub-boss corrupted by the elemental rift. Every journey is different, with procedurally-generated rooms, randomized loot, and punishing enemy encounters that reward tactical combat and quick reflexes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214320/extras/ef2320a02b05ce32474eb7becb6bd571.poster.avif?t=1770640008\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214320/extras/ef2320a02b05ce32474eb7becb6bd571.webm?t=1770640008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214320/extras/ef2320a02b05ce32474eb7becb6bd571.mp4?t=1770640008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your build, master your skills, and adapt to ever-changing layouts and enemy patterns. With multiple playstyles and randomized challenges in each run, <strong>Wartheon</strong> offers deep replayability for roguelike fans seeking skill-based progression and meaningful decision-making.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214320/extras/78771fe7aaa72a8b9ba56bafdfd2fa73.poster.avif?t=1770640008\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214320/extras/78771fe7aaa72a8b9ba56bafdfd2fa73.webm?t=1770640008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214320/extras/78771fe7aaa72a8b9ba56bafdfd2fa73.mp4?t=1770640008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Level-Up &amp; Character Stats</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, you will level-up when your yelow experience bar at bottom-left filled. When leveled-up, you will get a skill point and 2 stat points. You can use them in order to improve the chracter's build. Every character has 5 unique special skills. But you can only use 3 of them actively.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214320/extras/67f37957f41eae9b57e41df95240c883.poster.avif?t=1770640008\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214320/extras/67f37957f41eae9b57e41df95240c883.webm?t=1770640008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214320/extras/67f37957f41eae9b57e41df95240c883.mp4?t=1770640008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>NPC Rooms</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the wandering through the dungeon, you will rarely meet NPC rooms. Those NPCs can sell you goods or convince you to play gamble.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
